  "text": "Consider 10 targets moving radially outwards with constant velocity as shown in Fig. 9 . The multi-target filters used to test the new metric are the Gaussian mixture MeMBer filter [CITATION_1] and the Gaussian mixture PHD filter [CITATION_2] . We compare these two filters to demonstrate the inability of the OMAT metric to adequately indicate good and bad performance, and also to illustrate how the proposed OSPA metric resolves these inconsistencies.",
